{
  "stem": "14387.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had to go back to my mother-in-law's again, and again leave the next day and the same crying, tearful farewell.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Plane wasn't going to leave that day either.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to go back for the third time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember my sister-in-law calling out when we came to the door, Mother, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That means, they're coming again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can remember her standing there and calling, Mother, they're coming again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, the third day when we got to the airport, they said, well, we're not going to take off today either.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There's no-- can't possibly land and get fuel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we immediately called the Swedish embassy then, told them-- the Norwegian government, the people who had helped us make all these arrangements.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we told them what had happened and we're not going to be able to go.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, they said, you have to go because all the arrangements that you've made for you to go to New York, if you don't get to Moscow in time you're going to miss all the connections.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You have to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, we said, they won't let the planes-- they said, we're going to find out what's going on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They made arrangements for the plane to take less people and more fuel and not land to get fuel, and that's what happened.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We came to Moscow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were supposed to be in Moscow for three days, but there was no time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They made arrangements for an [INAUDIBLE] guy to meet us and we had to fill out some papers, some kind of formalities.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He took us someplace to get these all done.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We just got to the train, and they held up the train for two hours.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
